Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴風號叛亂了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:11.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,遲到之後 晴風號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,突然攻擊了 教官艦猿島號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好像 將其擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為何 會發展如此事態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,猿島號艦長 古庄教官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,處於昏迷狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,具體情況還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:32.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,學生艦叛亂 攻擊了猿島號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,猿島號沉沒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:37.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長及全體船員平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為何 我們成叛亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,先攻擊的是猿島號好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:45.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,就算你對我說也...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:48.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,知床同學 怎麼可能會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:54.11,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但...但是 為何會沉沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:56.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,明明用的 是訓練彈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,莫非 這也是演習的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,演習 怎麼會沈船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:03.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那麼 若故意沈船的話呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:08.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們在偶然間 得知了猿島號的黑暗秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.11,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,她開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:12.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們只是遲到好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:13.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你們都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:15.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們 什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不能就這樣 放你們走 砰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:20.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,被她們跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:24.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,唯這樣 與秘密一同沉入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:26.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全是妄想好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,話說 納沙同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:29.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你的平板的網路功能 關閉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:30.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 剛才艦長 下令時我就把它關了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:37.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不能用網路功能 其實挺不方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:40.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過現在被發現了也是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,抱歉 雖然會有些不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過到第二會合點 鳥島海域就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:50.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,鏈...鏈路船位 也切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,也…也就是說我們現在是通緝犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:57.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,剛成為高中生 卻變成罪犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:01.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這是騙人的吧 快點告訴我這是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,騙...騙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 立石同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:08.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:14.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,叫我鈴就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:16.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小...鈴
