Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:04:00.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真白 用跑的會跌倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:07.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,媽媽 姐姐 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.02,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真白 慢點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以前橫須賀的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以前 也像此處一樣對吧 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我想你在學校也學過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,日俄戰爭後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以甲烷水合物的開採為起因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.81,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,日本開始出現了地殼下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:30.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,在水淹的都市區域 建造了大型浮船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:34.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,變成了海上都市 海洋開發得到了發展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:40.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,於是日本成為了海洋大國對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為軍事用途 而被建造的許多艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,被轉為民用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但作為非戰爭 使用的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 開始由女性擔任了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那就是 藍色人魚的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,對吧 真霜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.21,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,而首位艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,就是你們的曾祖母哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:07.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,從那時開始 宗谷家的代代女性都成為了 藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,媽媽我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:14.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但媽媽我 下次將是最後的航行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,媽媽會成為藍色人魚的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我要培育 如同這遼闊的大海般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:30.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,充實而爽朗的生活 在海上的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我想成為那樣的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我要去 媽媽擔任老師的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我期待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:02.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,回想起來 那時開始 一直不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我總是運氣不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不料 初次航行也...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:18.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,後甲板 需要緊急修理才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這真是慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:24.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,1000% 真心帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,美海對野間同學 入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:29.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,等松同學有空的話 也來幫下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,神魂顛倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,與真知一起拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真想 發給妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:42.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,可是如今手機通訊 被禁止了唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:46.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,媛萌 百百 美海 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,損傷狀況 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:51.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,如你所見 要緊急修理才行呢 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,知道了 之後我會來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 好忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:03.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小麻 情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,都是因為 全速關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,需要進行全面檢修了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真是的 你太勉強它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小黑 抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,別叫得那麼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,能稱呼我 黒木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,明白了 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,完全沒明白好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那樣子 當艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小光 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,留奈與小空都沒受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,都記住名字了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:33.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不愧是 艦長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.29,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有 其它傷員對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那就好 但竟然發展成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴天霹靂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,今後要怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,智者不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,仁者不憂 勇者不畏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 請盡速回到艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,抱歉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,損傷情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:08.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,後甲板比較嚴重 深水炸彈還剩一發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,魚雷已經用完了 輪機室也要全面檢修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,別拍那種東西 給我去記錄損傷狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,學校方面有來聯繫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,該不會是把我們拋棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,或許他們正在確認情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:31.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,只...只要到鳥島附近10海浬處 就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:36.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯 我們被說成像叛亂 攻擊了猿島號一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,必須說明事情並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,會不會一到會合點 就被逮捕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你們 為何要攻擊猿島號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不是那樣的 先動手的是猿島號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你是說 她們不會相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但我們沒有叛亂的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,畢竟 我們無法繼續逃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,儘快 在附近的港口停泊吧 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:04.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,說的是呢 再說入港後 也不會受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:07.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小鈴 到橫須賀還要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,巡航速度38小時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:13.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真是的 進了垃圾班還要遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,什麼叫「垃圾班」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴風號或許是合格學生中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,最墊底那群人 被配屬的船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但這一點 你也一樣好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不准 拿我相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.77,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我入學考試 應該是所有問題都答對的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我只是答案 填寫錯在 下一欄框的答案上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真不走運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是...是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:44.21,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,像我 能考上都算是奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,碰巧複習過的內容 出現在題目上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,更別說 當艦長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這一位是擁有超好運氣的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:02.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這種時候 能像那樣回學校就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,無需氫氣或者氦氣的飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.81,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不知道能否做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.81,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那只是 空想的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,荒唐胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:16.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,各位 飯準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,今日的菜單是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴風咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,今天 是星期五呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那麼 輪班下去用餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們船的咖喱 會是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,泡浴與咖喱 先選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:40.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,當然是咖喱好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:41.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是咖喱對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,宗谷同學 我們一起去吃咖喱好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小黒 你不和我一起去 怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,右舷 060 距離3萬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,接近中的大型艦船...是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,格拉夫·施佩艦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,格拉夫·施佩艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,來自德國的留學生艦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,總之 全體就備戰部署
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全體就備戰部署
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以20節速度接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們被發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,似乎如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,施佩艦 主炮正在旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要攻擊我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,話...都不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,野間同學 舉白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,施佩艦 主炮開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:25.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,輪機不停掉 也不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,的確 僅掛白旗 不算投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但我們不是要逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.11,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯 右滿舵 轉向 180
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,右舵 滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,落彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,施佩艦 加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:58.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,快點逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,施佩艦 標準排水量12100噸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:10.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,資料顯示最高航速28.5節 28cm主炮6門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:14.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,15cm炮8門 魚雷發射管8門 最大裝甲160mm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不愧被稱為小型直教艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:20.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,擁有巡洋艦的船體及直教艦火力水準
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,落彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:26.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,主...主炮的最大射程 約3萬6千碼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:31.29,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,重達300kg的炮彈 以每分鐘2.5發的速度發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,就算只中一發 一瞬間都得被擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過就算15cm副炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,也比我們的主炮火力強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,火力及裝甲 對方占盡了優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:44.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我們比對方強的只有速度與靈活性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,輪機持續輸出 全馬力的話 會壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,發射魚雷 制止她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,已經 沒有魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,說起來 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,本艦火力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,70-5
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,射程7000m 穿深50mm？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,施佩艦的側舷裝甲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,80mm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,30
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,距離 縮短到3千碼 就能擊穿 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你們居然可以正常對話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這就是 做為艦長的才能嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小麻 能夠持續輸出的速度是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,最多第四戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:17.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,第四戰速 27節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:19.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,與對方的最大戰速 幾乎相同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,轉呀轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,轉呀轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小鈴 左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左..左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:32.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左舵30度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.10,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}躲進煙霧裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,正舵 右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,正舵 右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,右舵30度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,只要中一彈 就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:54.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,所以必須活用速度和轉向能力 繞著彎逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:57.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小麻 讓鍋爐不完全燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,了解 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,煙幕擋住她們的視線就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,然後 實施躲避運動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雖然 會對輪機造成負擔 總之拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,拜託 也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,但...也只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:12.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小鈴 改之航運動 不平衝轉速 可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不過 盡可能不要減速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:18.35,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要想攔住他們 只能用實彈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,戰鬥 左舷 炮擊 30度 目標 施佩艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:35.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,在說什麼 這與猿島號 那時候一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,用實彈打穿她們的艦艉大軸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這樣就能爭取時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 就真的變成叛亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:45.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這樣下去 會有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,實彈 裝彈開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,裝填完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,射擊準備 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要攻擊艦艦艉大軸 要接近到什麼距離比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:20.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,在水中 炮彈速度會急劇下降 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不是有水下彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:25.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那是 巡洋艦以上才有 我們沒有裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:28.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我聽說 普通彈在水中也能前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:32.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,理論上12.7cm炮彈 在水中前進距離約10公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:36.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,如果考慮 打穿側舷裝甲的最壞情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:39.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要接近到距離3千碼以內 才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,保持8字型航向的情況下 接近到3千碼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要接近嗎 我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,都說 我好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,請乖乖行駛過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,給我認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,距離4千碼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,3千8
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,3千6
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:19.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,有小艇 從施佩艦 向本艦行駛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小艇的乘員 落海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,她們在攻擊同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:37.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我不願意聽從艦長的命令 為什麼要攻擊晴風號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,你說什麼 你要違背艦長命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,該死 這艘破船 我要逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,別在那 胡思亂想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:48.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,對我來說 虛構比現實 更加真實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:49.50,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}相對距離700碼  相對速率20節...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:52.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,請稱呼 我為宗谷同學 或者副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.80,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這裡 可以拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,幫我牽制住德國艦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小幸 叫醫務委員 美波同學 來甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,為什麼 要去救敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,那不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,海上的同伴 都是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長 去救落海的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,接近到距離3千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,距離3千2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,3千1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:43.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,射擊 射擊 射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:47.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,二號炮 右舷 開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,目標命中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,施佩艦 減速中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,第四戰速（27節） 保持航向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,逃跑時...滿厲害的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,會沒事的 振作一點...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒事的 你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:02.29,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我只是 做出正確的指示而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以最大戰速（35節）脫離現在海域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小麻 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:16.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,鍋爐會壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,以後該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我不可以 一臉不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,因為 我是艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,對吧 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,美波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,她什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,沒有外傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,腦波也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,剩下 等她恢復意識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我會看著她的 美波同學你去用餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全身都是流汗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:28.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,終於 能舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我還以為 鍋爐會壞掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:35.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,接下來是 吃久等的咖喱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:38.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,來 大家請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,120% 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,這就是 晴風咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,終於可以吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:49.47,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,今天 吃咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嗯 因為 今天星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雖是甜口味 但有濃郁感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,因為我加了 藍莓醬做調味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.21,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.97,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我去給真知 也送一份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,她這是叫誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,美化委員長 你是黒木派嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.35,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,啊咧 宗谷同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不知道 不是在艦橋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,宗谷同學 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我給你拿來了 咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:31.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,不要太勉強自己
